(Worked Understanding) Tj
T*
(A good classroom illustration for Literature is a simple classroom example involving) Tj
T*
(Literature. When students can talk through that kind of example slowly and correctly,) Tj
T*
(they usually find it much easier to transfer the same reasoning to new questions.) Tj
